article.headline: Hickman puts up 25 in Bradley's 86-60 victory against Missouri State
article.description: — Connor Hickman's 25 points helped Bradley defeat Missouri State 86-60 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Hickman puts up 25 in Bradley's 86-60 victory against Missouri State
article.story: PEORIA, Ill. -- — Connor Hickman's 25 points helped Bradley defeat Missouri State 86-60 on Saturday night. Hickman also contributed six rebounds for the Braves (10-5, 2-2 Missouri Valley Conference). Darius Hannah scored 19 points and added five rebounds. Demarion Burch had 11 points and went 5 of 8 from the field. Cesare Edwards led the Bears (9-6, 1-3) in scoring, finishing with 17 points, seven rebounds and two steals. Donovan Clay added 13 points for Missouri State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
